author: Patrick Oppmann, CNN
title: Coronavirus-hit countries are asking Cuba for medical help. Why is the US opposed?
description: Cuba is sending doctors to more countries struggling with the coronavirus. But don't accept their help, the US State Department says.
content:
Havana (CNN)Cuba is offering to send doctors to more countries struggling with the coronavirus. But don't accept their help, the US State Department says.
